Steps to Install SASS:

1. Installed Node.js version 20.16 using nvm:
  - Ran: curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
  - Exited and reopened the terminal.
  - Installed Node.js with: nvm install 20.16
  - Verified with: node -v

2. Installed SASS using npm:
  - Ran: npm install -g sass@3.7.4
  - Verified SASS installation with: sass --version
